title: WTF | Watch: This is the best Marty McFly 'Back To The Future' costume you'll ever see
text:
Yes we've been so inundated with Back To The Future 'content' today that we almost wish the sequels never existed (but not really) but we all need to take a moment to salute this ingenious Marty McFly on a hoverboard costume.
If you haven't got your Halloween outfit sorted, you very well just may be a Hallowinner with this one.
Via YouTube
